    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 3,
    "last_activity_date" : 1562041530,
    "creation_date" : 1562041530,
    "answer_id" : 56845310,
    "question_id" : 52147706,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>To fix this issue, you must add to gradle:</p>\n\n<pre><code>implementation 'com.google.android.gms:play-services-measurement-impl:17.0.0'\nimplementation 'com.google.android.gms:play-services-ads:18.0.0'\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You can see comments from this <a href=\"https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/google-admob-ads-sdk/1OFaL07H5HU\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">link</a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 16209329,
      "reputation" : 1171,
      "user_id" : 11703772,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/2d8f44aaa0a89856b07c064634874ea6?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "John Doe",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/11703772/john-doe"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1562063330,
    "creation_date" : 1562063330,
    "answer_id" : 56850430,
    "question_id" : 52147706,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<blockquote>\n  <p>Try changing Proguard.cfg file to exclude obfuscating android.gms.*</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<pre><code>-keep public class com.google.android.gms.* { public *; }\n-dontwarn com.google.android.gms.**\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 312423,
      "reputation" : 5541,
      "user_id" : 626481,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 53,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/3794d1050184498ea47dd99638c30c65?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Hanry",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/626481/hanry"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1566209151,
    "creation_date" : 1566209151,
    "answer_id" : 57554552,
    "question_id" : 52147706,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Just upgrade the play-services-ads to <strong>18.1.1</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>implementation 'com.google.android.gms:play-services-ads:18.1.1'\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>As Described in <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/admob/android/rel-notes\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">release note</a></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Added dependencies on <strong>play-services-measurement</strong> and <strong>play-services-measurement-sdk</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Apps no longer need to add</strong> these dependencies explicitly.</p>\n"
  } ],
